Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,TENHO CHUUREN POUTOU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a ringer for me once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A chitoitsu.\N(all pairs hand)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He turns down each pair when he's got one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he read my discards?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting game you're having there, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you let me mix it up too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Change with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't beat this boomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't a problem, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful with all my heart for what you're doing, Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this changing shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd Game\NEast Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he have such faith that'll he'll complete his hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's extremely confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I start playing and after some hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can read the way the tiles are flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My chitoitsu hands have been called godlike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This sense of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what people have said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.\NA chitoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet another chitoitsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he win in this godly way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd Game\NEast Round 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can lay down my triplets as I complete them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason you have to be the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,showing your hand's progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in Tenpai.\NI'm not either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd Game\NEast Round 4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten is trying to provoke Murota and destroy his pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This style of playing, it's Murota's specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's entering his opponent's home turf,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and explicitly asking for a contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already in Tenpai.\NAs I thought, he's like a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What tile is he waiting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The dora is Red Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you put it, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This passed too!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've guessed it haven't you, Hiroyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A facade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a facade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This character's Mahjong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Mahjong of "giving up."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The weapon he uses in making players fold is his "image."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Making himself out to be a monster or a god
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To make players fold, he applies pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but progresses at his own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I did the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,his own pace started to freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pairs you've laid down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,are make believe.\NThey aren't all pairs at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,TanYao, SanSyoku\N(Only tiles 2-9, from 3 suits)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,7,700 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought not have been in Tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm so fucking dumb I'd tell you the composition of my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been playing in such a profoundly dishonest way
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you shouldn't be trusting anyone, should you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's continue, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd Game\NSouth Round 4
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in Tenpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point he's discarded a 1 and 2 Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was aiming for a SanSyoku or Tanyao\N(3 Suits, only tiles 2-8)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But he gave up on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's got an uneeded 4 Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That end tile there is the extra 4 Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten followed it with his eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph.\NHe just now deliberately followed that tile with his eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he think that'll make me feel safe and discard a 4 Pin or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect tsumo tile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can't discard the 4 Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten to one, Murota is waiting on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,T-ten! That's the tile Murota's waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He dealt into Murota's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That tile is a 4 Pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How?\NI could have sworn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He ought to have drawn the 4 Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how?\NCertainly, just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the jerk dew that very tile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How was that tile not a 4 Pin?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This Dora tile will be tough to discard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I break up a pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's like confessing I haven't got a single wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThat 8 Sou I thought was a 4 Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-he ought not be waiting on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At last... you look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,TanYao with one Dora\N3,900 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done it Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten certainly drew the 4 Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But in that instant he switched it for the 8 Sou he just drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all within his own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought. His Mahjong is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's as far as it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably won't be winning any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've... given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You retreated from a difficult position...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and you couldn't read your OWN mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true all the world round:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who crumble under pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,have no path to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you show this guy out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm retired too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairman is constrained for time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you somehow...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the stamina for long matches any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Murota just lost.\NThere's no one else but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Murota.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Some guy named Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they'll change a player for the next East South Round.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten, even though you were my opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd teach you something in front of "Hamada chan"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,something about ringers and the REAL world of Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi Shigeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is his Mahjong Strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Strong" isn't a sufficient word for what he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,During his career no one has been able to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Without doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,a man with the innate ability to blow others away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Until this day he hasn't lost a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A PEERLESS Mahjong professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahjong professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you know of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you retired?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about a strong player.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought I'd try to play him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NEast Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi Shigeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How on earth will he play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.\NIt's only just started,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but already the game's coming to a boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put, it's not just his lightning plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The man himself exudes a strange atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's indescribable, like something in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A brilliance that matches what's expected of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Overflowing with the strange and unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chanta with Red Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chanta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:57.85,cyan,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,102)}Chanta: All triples and pairs must contain a terminal tile [1 or 9] or honor[dragon or wind]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And furthermore completed on the 4th turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get my hand moving in only 4 turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You three guys have discarded 9 tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I drew 2 of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In total...\NIt felt like I drew eleven times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NEast Round 3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Another chanta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:18:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NEast Round 4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in Tenpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not his typical consecutive wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but once again he was going for a Chanta hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you play in a more normal style?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still measuring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Measuring?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mahjong I'm playing now does not depend upon luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In a 100 games
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll win 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Without knowing the general strength of your opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jumping in head first wouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NSouth Round 2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not Chanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought i'd swtich it up some.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NSouth Round 3
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got any character tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A... code?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:23:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.82,0:23:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If no one noticed I wouldn't know what I'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be sad playing with three worthless players.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.71,0:23:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Code?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.71,0:23:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki, you understand by now, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to now Akagi's hands have been largely Chanta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He told us which in his discards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The orientation of discarded character tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Upside down means Chanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right side up means it's not Chanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. This time it's Chanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.94,0:24:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up, bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just embarrassing yourself by talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for example, Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he stopped himself before declaring Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but you turned the character tile!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.62,0:24:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.62,0:24:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, when Akagi discarded the 9 Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any character tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think about that 9 Man, it was upside down, meaning chanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.42,0:24:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But, strictly speaking, 9 Man is not a character tile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.31,0:24:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore you could think it won't be chanta as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.42,0:24:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that at first glance...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.20,0:24:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll understand when you look at Akagi's open hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.62,0:24:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If he won with a 1 Sou he'd have Chanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.68,0:24:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,4 Sou and it wouldn't be Chanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.08,0:24:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's to say he could wait for both outcomes\NThe one you discarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.60,0:24:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid watching from the sidelines understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.02,0:25:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've therefore been playing with trash, haven't you Ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.68,0:25:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NSouth Round 4
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.51,0:25:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.82,0:25:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you get me something good?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.35,0:25:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is sushi okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.00,0:25:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sushi, hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.78,0:25:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You guise...\NThe most delicious thing in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.14,0:25:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.71,0:25:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal people probably say it's fugu or sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.17,0:25:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.15,0:25:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, when you play Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.14,0:25:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,men who will bet their entire fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.25,0:25:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.51,0:25:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they're playing a tile cut from their very soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.48,0:26:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A tile with a soul riding on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.51,0:26:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get a direct hit with that tile...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.31,0:26:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a feeling like devouring a person's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.71,0:26:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to that flavor...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.71,0:26:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fugu or sushi are as good as garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.91,0:26:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.91,0:26:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People's souls are the most delicious thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.05,0:26:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.02,0:26:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Baiman\N(24,000/16,000 points dealer/non-dealer)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.37,0:26:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a tough spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.17,0:26:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be perfectly summed up:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.68,0:27:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.54,0:27:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NAkagi just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.40,0:27:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see an opening once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.71,0:27:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He progresses with a near perfect game,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.17,0:27:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,HOWEVER
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.17,0:27:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep inside he's thinking this is a load of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.40,0:27:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.91,0:27:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What he wants most of all isn't winning by staring off into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.85,0:27:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.91,0:27:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is he wants a real fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.20,0:27:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He want's to go "all or nothing" more than anyone else.\NThis is Akagi's true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.31,0:27:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the ONLY chink to stab at that bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.54,0:27:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll aim for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.57,0:27:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.45,0:27:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.71,0:27:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
